http.html:
• Home

  • Contact us

John Beasley has been photographing racehorses for over 20 years. He has worked on racecourses throughout Great Britain and his images have been published in all of the UK National newspapers and in many magazines and books. Through his publishing company (Paleface Publications) he has published fourteen volumes of the 'big green annual' - a pictorial annual on point-to-point racing in Great Britain.

Some of John Beasley's recent images are now available to purchase as high quality prints. Click on the Events & Images link to view the image galleries.
